      <p>An <a href="ch60s13.html#MonstersIntro-A127">avoral's</a> bones are strong but hollow, so even the largest specimens weigh no more than 120 pounds. An <a href="ch60s13.html#MonstersIntro-A127">avoral</a> is about 7 feet tall. Each of an <a href="ch60s13.html#MonstersIntro-A127">avoral's</a> wings has a small hand at the midpoint. When the wings are folded, these appendages are about where human hands would be and can do nearly anything hands can do.</p>
      <p>An <a href="ch60s13.html#MonstersIntro-A127">avoral's</a> visual acuity is virtually unmatched: It can see detail on objects up to 10 miles away and is said to be able to discern the color of a creature's eyes at 200 paces.</p>
      <p><a href="ch60s13.html#MonstersIntro-A127">Avorals</a> speak Celestial, <a href="ch75.html#EpicMonsters(A-E)57">Infernal</a>, and Draconic, but can speak with almost any creature, thanks to their <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch51.html#SpellsT-Z12">tongues</a></em></span> ability.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
